snippet: Ryan Lochte swam three races in less than two hours Friday at the world championships in Barcelona, Spain, coming away with two gold medals.
abstract: Ryan Lochte swims three races in less than two hours at world championships in Barcelona, Spain, coming away with two gold medals and the top time in a semifinal.
lead_paragraph: Ryan Lochte swam three races in less than two hours Friday at the world championships in Barcelona, Spain, coming away with two gold medals.
